race.description: Thank You Noel Cuthbert F&M Handicap
race.comment: EDITING (6) at her top now and she gets a better setup today. Will race closer from the low draw and adept in all conditions. Genuine each way player. CHANGING COLOURS (3) above average mare with a stack of improvement to come. Attacked the line again when seventh over 1400m at Randwick. Key jockey change and a win looks imminent. AROHA STONE (8) impressed when scoring first-up at Beaumont (Newcastle). Sent to town when held up in the straight and was a total forgive when last over 1400m at Randwick. Gets map favours and expected to return to form. MISS HADES (1) back sharply in grade and not to be underestimated.
